<center><big><code><span style="color: white; text-shadow: 1px 4px 0 #969696, 1px 9px 5px #aba8a8; font-family:Overpass Mono;">'''Level 268''' is the 269<sup>th</sup> level of the Backrooms.</span></code></big></center>
